      "raw_text": "All but three of the men who\nwere discharged by the Washing\nton Water Power company for\njoining the Carmen's union were\nput back to work this morning.\nThe men go back as union men\nand the company agrees not to dis\ncriminate against union men in the\nfuture. The company does not\nagree to employ only union men.\nThe men returned to their old po-\nsitions and ranking. This means\nthat they will not have to go back"
